/div>\n                   </div>\n                </div>\n           </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kec_main_box\">\n<div id=\"gltd_box\" class=\"kec_content_main\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n     <div class=\"gltd_top clearfix\">\n     \n    <div id=\"vsb_content\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;text-align: justify;line-height: 32px\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family: arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(129, 136, 188)\">研究领域</span></b></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap\">数论</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap\"><b style=\"text-align: justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family: arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(129, 136, 188)\">教育背景</span></b></p>\n<p>2008-2012 学士 清华大学</p>\n<p>2012-2017 博士 哈佛大学</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 136, 188); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 21px;\"><b>科研经历</b></span></p>\n<p>2020-2023 助理教授 马里兰大学</p>\n<p>2017-2020 助理教授 哥伦比亚大学</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap\"><b style=\"text-align: justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family: arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(129, 136, 188)\">荣誉与奖励</span></b></p>\n<p>2020.12 ICCM 2020年最佳论文奖，金奖</p>\n<p>2018-2022首席研究员，NSF授予DMS-1802292</p>\n<p>2017.5 US Junior Oberwolfach Fellow</p>\n<p>2017.4 US Junior Oberwolfach Fellow</p>\n<p>2014哈佛大学教学优异证书</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap\"><b style=\"text-align: justify\"></b></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap\"><b style=\"text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: rgb(129, 136, 188)\">代表性论文</span></b></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">*Some of the PDFs linked below are more updated than the arxiv versions.</span></p>\n<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n <h5 style=\"font-family: Enriqueta, Dosis, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(6, 56, 93);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Preprints</span></h5>\n <li><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The stable trace formula for Shimura varieties of abelian type<br>(with Mark Kisin and Sug Woo Shin)<br></span><a href=\"https://yhzhumath.github.io/KSZ.pdf\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">[pdf]</span></a> <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2110.05381\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">[arxiv]</span></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Revision coming! To appear in <em>Ann. Math. Stud.</em></span></p></li>\n <h5 style=\"font-family: Enriqueta, Dosis, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(6, 56, 93);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Published</span></h5>\n <li><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The stabilization of the Frobenius-Hecke traces on the intersection cohomology of orthogonal Shimura varieties.<br></span><a href=\"https://yhzhumath.github.io/ast.pdf\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">[pdf]</span></a> <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1801.09404\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">[arxiv]</span></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><em>Astérisque</em> To appear.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></li>\n <li><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Stabilizers of irreducible components of affine Deligne-Lusztig varieties<br>(with Xuhua He and Rong Zhou)<br></span><a href=\"https://yhzhumath.github.io/stabilizer.pdf\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">[pdf]</span></a> <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2109.02594\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">[arxiv]</span></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><em>J. Eur. Math. Soc.</em> To appear.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></li>\n <li><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Twisted orbital integrals and irreducible components of affine Deligne-Lusztig varieties<br>(with Rong Zhou)<br></span><a href=\"https://yhzhumath.github.io/CJM_08_01_A03.pdf\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">[pdf]</span></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><em>Camb. J. Math.</em>, 8 (2020), No. 1, 149–241. </span><a href=\"https://dx.doi.org/10.4310/CJM.2020.v8.n1.a3\" class=\"external\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">doi:10.4310/CJM.2020.v8.n1.a3</span></a></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></li>\n <li><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Fine Deligne-Lusztig varieties and Arithmetic Fundamental Lemmas<br>(with Xuhua He and Chao Li)<br></span><a href=\"https://yhzhumath.github.io/fineDL.pdf\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">[pdf]</span></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><em>Forum Math. Sigma</em>, 7 (2019), E15. </span><a href=\"http://dx.doi.org/10.1017/fms.2019.45\" class=\"external\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">doi:10.1017/fms.2019.45 </span></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">(Open Access)</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></li>\n <li><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Arithmetic intersection on GSpin Rapoport-Zink spaces<br>(with Chao Li)<br></span><a href=\"https://yhzhumath.github.io/rzopub.pdf\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">[pdf]</span></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><em>Compos. Math.</em>, 154 (2018), No. 7, 1407-1440. </span><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1112/S0010437X18007108\" class=\"external\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">doi:10.1112/S0010437X18007108</span></a></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></li>\n <li><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Remarks on the arithmetic fundamental lemma<br>(with Chao Li)<br></span><a href=\"https://yhzhumath.github.io/AFLpub.pdf\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">[pdf]</span></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><em>Algebra Number Theory </em>, 11 (2017), No. 10, 2425-2445. </span><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.2140/ant.2017.11.2425\" class=\"external\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">doi:10.2140/ant.2017.11.2425</span></a></p></li>\n <h5 style=\"font-family: Enriqueta, Dosis, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(6, 56, 93);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Other Published Writings</span></h5>\n <li><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Report for the Oberwolfach workshop </span><a href=\"https://www.mfo.de/occasion/2134/www_view\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Automorphic Forms, Geometry and Arithmetic </span></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">(Aug 2021)<br></span><a href=\"https://yhzhumath.github.io/OWR_2021_39.pdf#page=57\" style=\"color: rgb(13, 115, 190); font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">[pdf]</span></a></p></li>\n <br>\n <li><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Proof of the arithmetic fundamental lemma in the minuscule case<br>(with Chao Li)<br></span><a href=\"https://yhzhumath.github.io/FJ.pdf#page=90\" styl